Name: Project Kickoff Meeting
Notes: Initial project kickoff with all stakeholders. Defined scope milestones and resource allocation.

Name: Requirements Gathering Phase
Notes: Collect and document all business requirements from stakeholders. Create user stories and acceptance criteria.

Name: API Architecture Design
Notes: Design RESTful API architecture with OpenAPI spec. Define endpoints authentication and rate limiting.

Name: Database Schema Design
Notes: Design normalized database schema with indexes and relationships. Include migration strategy.

Name: Sprint 1 Planning
Notes: Plan first development sprint. Assign tasks estimate points and set sprint goals.

Name: UI/UX Wireframes
Notes: Create low-fidelity wireframes for all main user flows. Include mobile responsive designs.

Name: Authentication System Implementation
Notes: Implement OAuth 2.0 with JWT tokens. Include refresh token rotation and secure session management.

Name: User Registration Flow
Notes: Build user registration with email verification. Include password strength validation.

Name: Dashboard Component Library
Notes: Build reusable React component library with Storybook documentation.

Name: Real-time Data Sync
Notes: Implement WebSocket-based real-time data synchronization across clients.

Name: Performance Baseline Testing
Notes: Establish performance baselines with load testing. Document current metrics.

Name: CI/CD Pipeline Setup
Notes: Configure GitHub Actions for automated testing linting and deployment.

Name: Error Monitoring Setup
Notes: Integrate Sentry for error tracking and alerting. Configure source maps.

Name: Data Migration Strategy
Notes: Plan data migration from legacy system. Create rollback procedures.

Name: User Dashboard MVP
Notes: Build minimum viable user dashboard with key metrics and navigation.

Name: API Rate Limiting
Notes: Implement token bucket rate limiting for API endpoints. Add Redis caching.

Name: Mobile Responsive Design
Notes: Ensure all components are fully responsive. Test on various device sizes.

Name: Search Functionality
Notes: Implement full-text search with Elasticsearch. Include filters and suggestions.

Name: Notification System Design
Notes: Design notification system architecture. Include email SMS and push channels.

Name: Code Review Guidelines
Notes: Document code review process and standards for the team.

Name: Logging Infrastructure
Notes: Set up centralized logging with ELK stack. Configure log aggregation.

Name: Unit Test Coverage
Notes: Achieve 80% unit test coverage for core business logic.

Name: Security Headers Implementation
Notes: Implement security headers CSP HSTS and XSS protection.

Name: Environment Configuration
Notes: Set up development staging and production environment configurations.

Name: API Versioning Strategy
Notes: Define API versioning strategy and deprecation policy.

Name: Feature Flag System
Notes: Implement feature flag system for gradual rollouts.

Name: User Analytics Integration
Notes: Integrate analytics for user behavior tracking. Set up dashboards.

Name: Accessibility Audit
Notes: Conduct WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility audit and fix issues.

Name: Documentation Site Setup
Notes: Set up documentation site with Docusaurus. Include API reference.

Name: Sprint 2 Planning
Notes: Plan Sprint 2 based on Sprint 1 velocity and learnings.
